        p3: `Hōʻike ka papahana i nā ʻano, nā mele, a me nā moʻolelo kūʻokoʻa i hoʻoulu ʻia e nā ʻāina a me ke aniau hoʻoilo o North Dakota. Kū ka papahana ma luna o ka haʻi moʻolelo mālie, ʻoluʻolu a palekana no nā keiki, a ʻaʻole ia e haʻi hou i nā moʻolelo kahiko o nā kānaka ʻōiwi a i ʻole ka moʻomeheu kahiko.`,
        p4: `Ua hana ʻia kēia papahana e kekahi mea kākau kūʻokoʻa i hoihoi i ka moʻomeheu, ka noʻonoʻo o nā keiki a me ka haʻi moʻolelo noʻonoʻo.`,
        p5: `Hana ka mea hana i ka kākau, ke mele a me nā manaʻo kiʻi e hana i nā moʻolelo e kōkua ana i ke ola ʻuhane o nā keiki.`,
        p6: `He papahana lōʻihi kēia.`,
    },
    tt: {
        title: "",
        p0: "",
        subtitle: "",
        p1: `🌨 Балалар өчен North Dakota`,
        p2: `North Dakota Fairytales — Paul Brian Mashkovtsev тарафыннан булдырылган кыш темасына багышланган балалар өчен оригиналь әкиятләр проекты.`,
        p3: `Проектка Төньяк Дакотаның кышкы табигате һәм атмосферасы илһамландырган персонажлар, җырлар һәм әкиятләр керә. Ул балалар өчен тыныч, җылы һәм куркынычсыз хикәяләүгә юнәлтелгән һәм тарихи фольклор яки җирле халык риваятьләрен кабатламый.`,
        p4: `Проект мәдәни мирас, балалар фантазиясе һәм уйланылган хикәяләү белән кызыксынучы мөстәкыйль автор тарафыннан булдырылган.`,
        p5: `Автор текст, музыка һәм визуаль образлар белән эшли, балаларның эмоциональ халәтен яхшыртуга ярдәм итүче әсәрләр тудыра.`,
        p6: `North Dakota Fairytales — озак вакытка исәпләнгән иҗади проект.`,
    },
};

const t = text[lang as keyof typeof text] || text.en;
const pageTitle =
    (i18nText as any).old_snow_hub_meta_title ||
    "Welcome to North Dakota | North Dakota for Kids | Calm Winter Stories & Songs";
const pageDescription =
    (i18nText as any).old_snow_hub_meta_desc ||
    "Calm winter stories, songs, and gentle North Dakota nature themes for children — original tales and music from North Dakota Fairytales.";
---

<BaseLayout lang={lang}
    title={pageTitle}
    description={pageDescription}
    supplementaryLdJson={oldSnowWinterProgramJsonLd()}
    videoObject={showOldSnowSongSearch
        ? {
              name: currentSchema.name,
              description: currentSchema.description,
              thumbnailUrl: currentVideoThumbUrl,
              embedUrl: currentVideoEmbedUrl,
              contentUrl: currentVideoContentUrl,
              uploadDate: normalizeVideoUploadDate("2026-04-19"),
          }
        : undefined}
    isAuthorPage={true}>

    <h2>{t.subtitle}</h2>

    <div class="intro-card">
        <p>{t.p0}</p>

        <p>{t.p1}</p>
        {showOldSnowSongSearch ? (
            <div class="song-video-container relative mx-auto w-fit">
                <Video
                    src={currentVideoUrl}
                    title="Welcome to North Dakota song"
                    class="song-video-frame"
                />
                <a
                    href={searchHref}
                    aria-label={searchLabel}
                    title={searchLabel}
                    class="search-video-btn"
                    style="width: 150px !important; height: 150px !important;"
                >
                    <img
                        src={musicIcon.src}
                        alt={snowyMusicAlt}
                        class="w-[150px] h-[150px] object-contain search-video-icon"
                        style="width: 150px !important; height: 150px !important; min-width: 150px; min-height: 150px;"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                    <span
                        class="search-video-label text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight uppercase text-[#b3e5fc] drop-shadow-[0_2px_12px_rgba(255,255,255,0.7)] whitespace-nowrap"
                        style="color: #b3e5fc !important;"
                        dir={["ar", "fa", "ur"].includes(lang ?? "") ? "rtl" : "ltr"}
                    >
                        {snowyMusicLabel}
                    </span>
                </a>
            </div>
        ) : null}
        {showOldSnowSongSearch ? (
            <>
                <div class="song-lyrics-toggle-wrap">
                    <button
                        type="button"
                        class="song-lyrics-toggle-btn"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="song-lyrics-content"
                        data-lyrics-toggle
                    >
                        {lyricsToggleText}
                    </button>
                </div>
                <section id="song-lyrics-content" class="song-lyrics-content" hidden>
                    <h3 class="song-lyrics-title">{lyricsContent.title}</h3>
                    {lyricsContent.sections.map((section) => (
                        <article class="song-lyrics-section">
                            <h4>{section.label}</h4>
                            {section.lines.map((line) => (
                                line ? <p>{line}</p> : <div class="song-lyrics-break" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                            ))}
                        </article>
                    ))}
                </section>
            </>
        ) : null}
        <p>{t.p2}</p>
        <p>{t.p3}</p>
        <div class="old-snow-album-row" dir="ltr">
            <div class="old-snow-album-side old-snow-album-side--left">
                <a href={animalsHref} class="animals-btn">
                    {nav.animals}
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="old-snow-album-center">
                <img
                    src="/images/nd_animals_old.png"
                    alt="Cute winter animals playing in the snow in North Dakota | Animales de invierno jugando en la nieve en Dakota del Norte | Animaux d’hiver jouant dans la neige dans le Dakota du Nord | حيوانات شتوية لطيفة تلعب في الثلج في نورث داكوتا"
                    class="nd-image old-snow-album-img"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="old-snow-album-side old-snow-album-side--right">
                <a href={famousHref} class="famous-btn">
                    {nav.famous}
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p>{t.p4}</p>
        <img 
          src="/images/nd_old.png" 
          alt="Winter farm in North Dakota with northern lights and snow landscape | Granja invernal en Dakota del Norte con auroras y nieve | Ferme hivernale dans le Dakota du Nord avec aurores boréales et neige | مزرعة شتوية في نورث داكوتا مع الشفق القطبي والثلج"
          class="nd-image"
        />
        <p>{t.p5}</p>
        <p>{t.p6}</p>



</div>

<script>
  const lyricsToggleButton = document.querySelector("[data-lyrics-toggle]");
  const lyricsContent = document.getElementById("song-lyrics-content");

  if (lyricsToggleButton && lyricsContent) {
    lyricsToggleButton.addEventListener("click", () => {
      const isExpanded = lyricsToggleButton.getAttribute("aria-expanded") === "true";
      lyricsToggleButton.setAttribute("aria-expanded", String(!isExpanded));
      lyricsContent.hidden = isExpanded;
    });
  }
</script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .song-video-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
  }

  .song-video-frame {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(10, 22, 38, 0.35);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .search-video-btn {
    position: absolute;
    right: -235px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    display: block;
    z-index: 50;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .search-video-icon {
    display: block;
  }

  .search-video-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(100% + 14px);
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    text-align: center;
    width: max-content;
  }


  .song-lyrics-toggle-wrap {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 1rem auto 1.75rem auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .song-lyrics-toggle-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(206, 196, 222, 0.45);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: #f5f8ff;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(128, 145, 173, 0.4), rgba(104, 121, 150, 0.33));
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(10, 22, 38, 0.2);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .song-lyrics-toggle-btn:hover {
    background-color: rgba(90, 108, 140, 0.5);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(10, 22, 38, 0.25);
  }

  .song-lyrics-toggle-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid rgba(236, 244, 255, 0.9);
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .song-lyrics-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.2rem auto;
    color: #dce4f1;
  }

  .song-lyrics-title {
    margin: 0 0 1.6rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    color: #ecf2fc;
  }

  .song-lyrics-section {
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background-color: rgba(47, 64, 93, 0.2);
  }

  .song-lyrics-section h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem 0;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #f3f7ff;
  }

  .song-lyrics-section p {
    margin: 0.2rem 0;
    color: #d9e2f2;
  }

  .song-lyrics-break {
    height: 0.7rem;
  }

  [dir="rtl"] .intro-card,
  [dir="rtl"] .intro-card p,
  [dir="rtl"] .song-lyrics-content,
  [dir="rtl"] .song-lyrics-section,
  [dir="rtl"] .song-lyrics-section p {
    direction: rtl;
    text-align: right;
    unicode-bidi: plaintext;
  }

  .nd-image {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 650px;
    display: block;
    margin: 30px auto;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  /* Equal-width side tracks (flex: 1 1 0) keep the image column in the true horizontal center */
  .old-snow-album-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 30px auto;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .old-snow-album-side {
    flex: 1 1 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .old-snow-album-side--left {
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding-right: 75px;
  }

  .old-snow-album-side--right {
    justify-content: flex-start;
    padding-left: 75px;
  }

  .old-snow-album-center {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .old-snow-album-row .old-snow-album-img {
    margin: 0;
    width: min(100%, 650px);
    max-width: 650px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .old-snow-album-row {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      row-gap: 75px;
    }

    .old-snow-album-side {
      flex: 1 1 100%;
      justify-content: center !important;
      padding-right: 0 !important;
      padding-left: 0 !important;
    }

    .old-snow-album-side--left {
      order: 2;
    }

    .old-snow-album-center {
      order: 1;
      flex: 1 1 100%;
    }

    .old-snow-album-side--right {
      order: 3;
    }
  }

  /* Same capsule metrics as global .ndf-home-btn (BaseLayout.astro): padding, radius, shadow, transition */
  .animals-btn,
  .famous-btn {
    flex: 0 1 auto;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    width: min(100%, 440px);
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(206, 196, 222, 0.4);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #ffffff;
    background-color: rgba(181, 168, 203, 0.25);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .animals-btn:hover,
  .famous-btn:hover {
    background-color: rgba(181, 168, 203, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    border-color: rgba(220, 212, 232, 0.55);
  }

  .animals-btn:focus-visible,
  .famous-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }
</style>